<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1724,1856]" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">
The description of the carapace, live colour and habitat, “in sweet-water creeks” (
<bibRefCitation author="Curtiss" box="[1071,1275,1724,1748]" firstAuthor="Curtiss" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" pagination="1 - 193" refId="ref10067" refString="Curtiss, A. (1938) A short zoology of Tahiti in the Society Islands. Guide Printing, Brooklyn, New York, pp. i - xvi, 1 - 193." type="book chapter" year="1938">
Curtiss 
<number box="[1160,1220,1724,1748]" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" value="1938.0">1938</number>
: 
<number box="[1232,1275,1724,1748]" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" value="176.0">176</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) easily identifies this species with 
<taxonomicName authority="(Fabricius, 1798)" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1798" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1798" box="[413,808,1759,1784]" class="Malacostraca" family="Varunidae" genus="Varuna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="litterata">
<emphasis box="[413,597,1760,1784]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">Varuna litterata</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius" box="[617,800,1759,1783]" firstAuthor="Fabricius" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" refId="ref10711" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1798) Supplementum Entomologiae Systematicae. Proft et Storch, Hafniae, 572 pp." type="book" year="1798">
Fabricius, 
<number box="[743,800,1759,1783]" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" value="1798.0">1798</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName authorityName="H.Milne Edwards" authorityYear="1837" box="[828,948,1759,1783]" class="Malacostraca" family="Varunidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Varunidae</taxonomicName>
), a species common in 
<collectingCountry box="[1237,1436,1759,1783]" name="French Polynesia" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">French Polynesia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Poupin &amp; Juncker" box="[158,433,1796,1820]" firstAuthor="Poupin" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" refId="ref12808" refString="Poupin, J. &amp; Juncker, M. (2010) Guide des Crustaces Decapodes du Pacifique Sud (A guide to the decapod crustaceans of the South Pacific). Secretariat of the Pacific Community, CRISP (Coral Reef Initiatives for the Pacific), 317 pp." type="book" year="2010">
Poupin &amp; Juncker 
<number box="[372,433,1796,1820]" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" value="2010.0">2010</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). An allied species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Hwang &amp; Takeda, 1986" authorityName="Hwang &amp; Takeda" authorityYear="1986" box="[661,1005,1796,1821]" class="Malacostraca" family="Varunidae" genus="Varuna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yui">
<emphasis box="[661,724,1797,1820]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">V. yui</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Hwang &amp; Takeda" box="[732,1005,1796,1821]" firstAuthor="Hwang" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" pagination="11" refId="ref11435" refString="Hwang, J. - J. &amp; Takeda, M. (1986) A new freshwater crab of the family Grapsidae from Taiwan. Proceedings of the Japanese Society of Systematic Zoology, 33, 11 - 18." type="journal article" year="1986">
Hwang &amp; Takeda, 
<number box="[946,1005,1796,1820]" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" value="1986.0">1986</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, also occurs in the western part of the Pacific, but this species does not reach so far east (
<bibRefCitation author="Ng" box="[718,818,1831,1855]" firstAuthor="Ng" journalOrPublisher="Department of Zoology, National University of Singapore, Shinglee Press, Singapore" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" pagination="1 - 156" refId="ref12314" refString="Ng, P. K. L. (1988) The freshwater crabs of Peninsular Malaysia and Singapore. Department of Zoology, National University of Singapore, Shinglee Press, Singapore, pp. i - viii, 1 - 156, Figs. 1 - 63, 4 colour plates." title="The freshwater crabs of Peninsular Malaysia and Singapore" type="book chapter" year="1988">
Ng 
<number box="[760,818,1831,1855]" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" value="1988.1998">1988</number>
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ng, P. K. L." box="[830,890,1831,1855]" editor="Carpenter, K. E. &amp; Niem, V. H." journalOrPublisher="FAO, Rome" pageId="9" pageNumber="52" pagination="1045 - 1155" refId="ref12368" refString="Ng, P. K. L. (1998) Crabs. In: Carpenter, K. E. &amp; Niem, V. H. (eds.), FAO species identification guide for fishery purposes. The living marine resources of the Western Central Pacific. Vol. 2. Cephalopods, crustaceans, holothurians and sharks. FAO, Rome, pp. pp. 1045 - 1155." title="Crabs" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="FAO species identification guide for fishery purposes. The living marine resources of the Western Central Pacific. Vol. 2. Cephalopods, crustaceans, holothurians and sharks" year="1998">1998</bibRefCitation>
).
